metadata.dc:author: Pena Outeiriño, J M
Leal López, A
metadata.dc:description: In the already scarce traumatic ureter pathology, beyond the scope of Gynaecology, we present a case, also iatrogenic, which although it is described as a possible complication in the performing of a translumbar aortography, is of unquestionable interest by virtue of its origin and subsequent evolution.
metadata.dc:title: Traumatismo ureteral postaortografía translumbar.
[Ureteral injuries following translumbar aortography].
